      <div class="about-text">
        <p><strong>Computer Science & Engineering student at Lovely Professional University</strong> passionate about transforming complex datasets into clear, actionable insights.</p>
        <p>My toolkit spans <strong>Python, SQL, Power BI, and Excel</strong> — I've built dashboards that visualized 20,000+ villages across Jharkhand and analyzed 100K+ rows of customer satisfaction data.</p>
        <p>Beyond analytics, I hold <strong>Oracle Cloud Infrastructure certifications</strong> in AI Foundations and Data Science, and I've competed in university-level hackathons.</p>
